        "applies_to": "primary",
        "calculation": "minimum_total",
        "note_md": {
          "en": "Current minimum for all sectors except financial services; the threshold increases progressively with age and financial services has a higher threshold.",
          "zh-Hans": "目前除金融服务业外所有行业的最低标准；随着年龄的增长，门槛逐渐提高，金融服务的门槛也更高。"
        }
      }
    ],
    "accepted_sources": ["employment"],
